<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201210/94e901d80913402a9372fc5154d97608.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>连踢着拖孩的包租公都把它当饭堂！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201210/8c3523d8a00143d2beb09e8d036e35dc.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">快拍一拍你身边的上班族还有家人朋友，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">以后有更好的的选择啦！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201210/8ab4aca1ec384bd7ab1b51608556c114.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>01</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>// 邻家的湘菜小馆，温暖实惠 //</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>好好呷！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▧ 烟火里的生活滋味 ▧</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201210/94e901d80913402a9372fc5154d97608.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201210/309a932676424fb5b402e03c07043b64.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">● ● ●</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201210/3e0f46eb22ae4ff58011cc8cb4186407.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一进店便看见<strong>横在大厅中央的明档，</strong>尽是<strong>热气腾腾的美食</strong>，小哥哥捧着饭桶为客人添饭...大家就像亲戚家人/朋友邻里之间一样，简简单单地吃着饭。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201210/bdd1ff511c574384a4088a6e9f03b9f4.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201210/26a8c2fda17541b1873db683c1b356ec.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">将历史感的环境生活化，<strong>伴着烟火气和湖南花鼓戏的氛围用餐，热热闹闹，没有拘束</strong>。即使一个人来，也能随意自在。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▧ 用良心做菜▧</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201210/ae7faebf50e84035a0d5643ebb1a1cf3.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">装潢并不奢华，菜品选择也不算很多，<strong>全是老口子记忆里的家常味</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>02</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>// 这些经典，在广州的湖南人都懂 //</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>好好呷！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▧ 剁椒活鱼头 ▧</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201210/ad60c76130624bd8ac88dc1ea0137d6d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">如果提起<strong>湖南的代表菜</strong>，剁椒鱼头必须拥有姓名，湖南人无论走到哪里，<strong>都会想念它的味道</strong>。好呷的鱼头所取部位极大，<strong>和小伙伴一起分享够够的！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">❶ Fresh</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>鲜活大鱼头，老让师傅挨打！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201210/fabb36c83bd6479d8bf7359d3ea9f038.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>“好生勐！”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201210/f8da7ba59d47486eb35b8c3136504157.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">不整那些虚头巴脑的，要做就用良心做。这里的每一锅剁椒鱼头，<strong>只选生勐蹦跶的大头鱼</strong>（师傅分分钟被扇耳光！），3斤重左右才能入锅，现点现捞，<strong>要多新鲜有多新鲜！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201210/b275dc2af0e84029954b180b27e50096.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201210/da318ff6db00480b9a7eb97a7f9e8dca.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201210/6a928708d58442b3952c4e86de503a53.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>做法地道也极为讲究，</strong>将处理干净的整个鱼头部分，抹盐撒料入高汤，此时就差最后注入灵魂的一步。看似简单的剁椒鱼头，<strong>用料和工序可多了！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">➋ Exclusive Secret Recipe</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>独家秘制剁椒酱 </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201210/2d839955fd814ccfa7ec8966d866e6e9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201210/d138de21d3a94a54b867387cc6ad2fd5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201210/d138de21d3a94a54b867387cc6ad2fd5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201210/d138de21d3a94a54b867387cc6ad2fd5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">“辣”是湖南人的性格，普通的剁椒可入不了老板的眼，<strong>独家秘制的手工剁椒酱料，咸鲜不呛辣，</strong>包你吃了还想吃！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">➌ Just 5 minutes</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>5分钟高温现煮，嫩滑不老 </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201210/94e901d80913402a9372fc5154d97608.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201210/8aa7d1e2b22c47528e29bf85d1766991.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>新鲜的鱼头必须现煮才不算浪费，</strong>现场调好味后，掐准计时器，5分钟不多不少！高温烹煮而不流失营养，<strong>鱼头嫩滑不老</strong>，袅袅炊烟中难免叫人期待！撒上增香的葱花，上桌！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">➍ Still Hot</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>明火上桌，保持热度 </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201210/7051a1e5cc474a07941f668881758937.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">鱼头上桌依然带着明火继续沸腾保温，<strong>香气伴随着每一次“咕嘟咕嘟”声不断释放，</strong>一开盖小伙伴们就已经忍不住了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">➎ Special Methods</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>先吃鱼头后烫菜 </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201210/52a7d67dce7e4450ac535594969930b1.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201210/49c578a1e5fa4343a9adabb44f68ef11.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">● ● ●</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201210/f61eb10f01354f4ca34f41b43715b20c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">鱼头吸收了鲜辣爽口的汤汁，<strong>肉质鲜嫩细腻又多汁，</strong>关键是<strong>辣度也很友好</strong>，原本是湖南民间再家常不过的美味，在一番秘制酱料的“调教”下，<strong>好好呷！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201210/48ba166b0d52450d84044027f8e256cf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">整个鱼头尤其是带骨的皮肉，<strong>一吸熘便滑入口中，</strong>哎哟喂，<strong>简直不要太嫩！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201210/701bec09eb464d1d82b4122607a12d69.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">剁椒鱼头普遍千篇一律，但好呷的活鱼头则有灵魂吃法！<strong>先吃鱼头，后烫配菜</strong>（没错，可以下配菜的！）伊面、酸菜、豆皮...吸饱了鱼鲜和剁椒的咸香。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>//</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201210/9dbbbe2d87d44f3ca70492c70d359802.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">点上一份伊面或者白米饭，就算吃光了鱼肉，<strong>伴着汤汁都能把整个锅吃光！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>03</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>// 道道下饭，分量良心包你饱 //</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>好好呷！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201210/2f98da3258d447e89ef0d05a9ab2fc76.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">好呷的每一道菜都超能打，<strong>直接把巨下饭打在公屏上！</strong>轻轻松松吃上两碗饭<strong>，</strong>分量管饱，实在超值！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▧ 小炒黄牛肉 ▧</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201210/e4b6f8c89d05454b94a0494ac57db82d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">小炒黄牛肉<strong>堆成小山似的，</strong>湖南人果然就是豪横！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201210/0f7530b01ab84ab997a88ffcc729d53c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">手工鲜切的黄牛肉，<strong>保留了镬气的同时富含更多汁水，</strong>料头的香气统统被吸进肉里。几勺汤汁就能吃下一碗饭，好呷！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▧ 软嫩牛腩煲 ▧</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201210/74b74f23de544f3297dfb91f3c9866e0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这牛腩煲，<strong>焖得软而不烂</strong>，自带湘娃子的火辣属性，入口立即醒神！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201210/48b0f1b9f6024dd1b2230108a1f11d45.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">牛腩特意不切成大方块，<strong>一口一块，易嚼不塞牙，</strong>酱汁肆意地在口中穿梭！萝卜也意外地出色，<strong>汁水丰盈入味，一抿就化，</strong>老广也盖章认可！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▧ 酸辣带劲下饭菜 ▧</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201210/d6568e82c18643f3a9521b33248f09cb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201210/8318c93d8c2d493393d14ab3f8031641.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201210/0e9f5c65e5724bb990e45b6e3143dddd.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201210/c3a83d970aad47fe8ac66651756cbee6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">每日现卤的牛肉，<strong>那色泽，一看就入足了味！</strong>爽口的酸豆角搭配脆嫩鸡杂，<strong>用料一点都不含煳，绝了！</strong>一秒变身无情的碳水收割机。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▧ 湘西人的儿时经典菜 ▧</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201210/7be50afe12ff48be8c3c9c34dd824bb8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201210/f8e71c26a41648f7bcfc5550e7f50872.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201210/cd907a485d144d2eb3bdf21f543fc0e8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">最想念的是外婆菜，搭配金黄的土鸡蛋，<strong>咸、酸、辣、脆各种滋味在嘴里绽放！</strong>还有超赞的盐蛋黄油麦菜，<strong>蛋黄沙沙的口感</strong>大大丰富了油麦菜的咀嚼层次，好家伙！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▧ 手工现搓糖油粑粑 ▧</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201210/ad07e026899b4be7af9d9d7ca21b2c9e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>经典湖南的小吃名片之一的糖油粑粑，</strong>像肉嘟嘟的小胖子在沸腾的锅中翻滚着，晶莹亮泽看着就甜丝丝~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201210/9a94de91b86247e5bf4943ec503fb45b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">糖油粑粑<strong>吃起来糯叽叽的</strong>，撒上桂花<strong>增添了一丝淡淡的清香</strong>。咀嚼的瞬间，<strong>沁着糖汁儿的香甜，</strong>大脑也不自觉地分泌出愉悦的多巴胺~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201210/bc2a227905e24f27b1ec2d6f0461d585.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201210/bc2a227905e24f27b1ec2d6f0461d585.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201210/bc2a227905e24f27b1ec2d6f0461d585.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201210/62533dd7bd9f4419b039f131f0468064.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>好呷剁椒活鱼头（百信店）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">📍店铺地址:</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">白云区棠乐路百信广场西区1楼L1-037铺</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">（优衣库楼上）</p>
